snippet.title: Clouzy! Showcase of Wholesome Games - Large
snippet.description:
Clouzy! is a farm game where you raise clouds in your own floating island to fill the world with positive emotions.

Here you can see some gameplay of our current project, Clouzy!.
Hope you like it!
